.panel.panel-warning.lead
  .panel-heading
    %h1.panel-title
      %strong NOTICE:
      Recent changes to GINA::ID
  .panel-body
    %p
      We've recently upgraded the GINA::ID application with a new more secure account managmenet system.

    %p
      As part of the upgrade your account was automatically migrated and no futher actions are required.
      If you encounter any problems, please #{mail_to 'support@gina.alaska.edu', 'email us at support@gina.alaska.edu'} and include description of the problem and what you were attempting to do when the problem occured.

    .text-right
      = link_to confirm_migration_user_path(current_user), class: 'btn btn-primary' do
        Dismiss notice
